Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.76,0:00:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}哟 里维
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.68,0:00:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你有没有长高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.89,0:00:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你好像没怎么变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.56,0:00:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}肯尼！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.93,0:02:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是枪声
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.01,0:02:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.22,0:02:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}别出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}希斯特莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.53,0:02:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}艾连
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.47,0:02:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}可恶 我们的行动完全被看穿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.23,0:03:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}肯尼 为什么偏偏是他这种人进了宪兵团
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.25,0:03:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是里维 调查兵团的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.84,0:03:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}可恶 这样下去我的部下跟艾连还有希斯特莉亚就都没了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.64,0:03:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这家店里似乎传出一股肮脏老鼠的恶臭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.86,0:03:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是只个头矮小的老鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.73,0:03:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}找到你了 宪兵大人来歼灭反派了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.36,0:03:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}砰！砰！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}什么嘛 居然不在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我在这里肯尼 好久不见了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}没想到你还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.54,0:04:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你杀了这么多宪兵 居然自己当上了宪兵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.42,0:04:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你这种小屁孩怎么可能懂大人的隐情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.34,0:04:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}哎呀 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.93,0:04:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}虽然你个头小 但岁数也不小了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.93,0:04:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我一直很期待你的活跃表现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}没想到我教会你的处世手段 竟然会以这种形式派上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.69,0:04:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我有没有教过你一个词叫瓮中之鳖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.03,0:04:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这个情况下不管你往哪里逃都会被上面的人一枪干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.66,0:04:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我说啊 里维
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.08,0:04:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我总算有点理解你为什么会当调查兵了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.88,0:04:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们都只能活在垃圾堆里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.22,0:04:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}光是像那样活着就已经拼上全力了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:04:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但当某一天知道世界原来如此广阔的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}肯定会深受伤害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.31,0:05:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但是 我们还有救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.35,0:05:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那就是找到了想做的事 很单纯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.61,0:05:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}道理虽然单纯 但实际上丰富了人生的就是兴趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.53,0:05:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}兴趣吗 轰飞我部下的头也是你的兴趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.83,0:05:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是啊 为了伟大的目标我可以大开杀戒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你不也在为了自己而杀戮不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.42,0:05:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.72,0:05:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}等等 是队长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.64,0:05:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}帮大忙了 老爷子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.69,0:05:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}椅子？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.57,0:05:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}开枪！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.83,0:06:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}有枪声
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.37,0:06:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}快听 响了好几下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}果然是发生了什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.63,0:06:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}大概是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.13,0:06:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}兵长的留言是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}接下来不只是跟巨人战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.01,0:06:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}还要跟人类战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.60,0:06:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}什么 这意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.81,0:06:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.81,0:06:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}刚才的是中央宪兵吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}师团长 请确认资料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.95,0:06:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}队长 你终于死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.91,0:06:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}蠢贷 死人怎么回答你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.04,0:06:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}痛痛痛 被算计了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.46,0:06:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}说起来酒馆等地方允许以自卫为目的合法持枪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.46,0:06:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}看来小矮子也多少有些成长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.09,0:06:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.26,0:07:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}啊？哪里好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我的梦想岂不是要泡汤了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.10,0:07:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}喂 是艾连他们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.48,0:07:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}兵长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.07,0:07:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那东西是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.46,0:07:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}追上那辆马车！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.46,0:07:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.92,0:07:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}听好了 那些家伙很熟悉对人战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.84,0:07:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们已经有三人被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.38,0:07:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}为了夺回艾连他们 千万不能犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}该下杀手就下杀手 懂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.97,0:07:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.94,0:07:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}阿尔敏 让
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.98,0:07:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}上马车 其他人掩护
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:07:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.49,0:08:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}又有人被…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}让
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.91,0:08:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}别动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.37,0:08:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.92,0:08:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}让！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs16\an9\1c&H0080FF&}现在可以公开的情报\N对人立体机动装置\N并非是为了驱逐巨人，\N而是为了和人类战斗\N作为立体机动装置的应对手段而开发。\N可以做出超越人类感知的行动速度\N以及从死角发起攻击\N在城市与森林地带能够发挥巨大的威力。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei} 王都 密特拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.69,0:08:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}没想到艾尔文那边会一无所获啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.15,0:08:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}如果无法查明艾连·叶卡和希斯特莉亚的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.91,0:08:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}停止调查兵团的活动也毫无意义啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.37,0:08:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那关于他们从尼克神父身上获取了多少情报这件事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}没办法 如果我们继续强行介入
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}也许会把一些他们尚未查明的情报泄露出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.46,0:09:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不 不管他们知道与否
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.72,0:09:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}只要知道他们在调查就已经足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.18,0:09:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}根据人类宪章把他们处理掉就行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.14,0:09:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就像我们一直以来采取的手段一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.90,0:09:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是雷斯卿的信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.53,0:09:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}似乎是已经抓到了艾连和希斯特莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}而且他们也已经对艾尔文跟调查兵团采取了手段
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们没有必要行动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.83,0:09:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这样一来就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.62,0:09:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}如果需要我们归还私人物品 就请在之后申请
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.75,0:09:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不 没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.34,0:09:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我有些话要跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.84,0:09:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我可不想听你讲回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}真冷淡啊 奈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.30,0:09:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们不是一起立志进入调查兵团的同伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.06,0:09:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这个小小的世界正渴望着变革
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这是希望 还是绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.48,0:10:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}中央值不值得我们将人类的未来托付给它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}作出选择的是谁 谁会被选上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.28,0:10:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你到底相信着谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.66,0:10:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}艾尔文 你到底要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.37,0:10:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}习以为常的孤注一掷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.01,0:10:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}三笠也有过这种经历吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.59,0:10:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.93,0:10:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.31,0:10:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.49,0:10:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}糟了 阿尔敏 让！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不行 先撒退！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.64,0:11:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}艾连！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}怎么了 在这么脏的地方吃不下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.11,0:11:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}让 我有件事想不通
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.54,0:11:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我开枪救你的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.71,0:11:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}说实话我以为已经来不及了 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但是 为什么是我先开的枪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.59,0:11:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.30,0:11:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}敌人在开枪前犹豫了一瞬闻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.35,0:11:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.02,0:12:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}阿尔敏 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.85,0:12:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我本应该立刻下手的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我杀掉的肯定是一个温柔的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.74,0:12:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是一个比我更有人性的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}而我却立刻扣动扳机了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.12,0:12:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}阿尔敏 你的双手已经沾上鲜血了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你再也变不回从前的你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.67,0:12:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}为什么你要说这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.13,0:12:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}接受新的自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.22,0:12:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}如果你没有弄脏自己的双手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.14,0:12:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}现在让就不会坐在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你之所以会立刻扣动扳机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.06,0:12:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是因为你的同伴马上就要被杀死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}阿尔敏 正因为你肯玷污自己的双手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们才没有失去一位同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.95,0:12:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.96,0:13:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}里维兵长 我本认为和人战斗是错误的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.09,0:13:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}突然间命令我们去杀人的兵长也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.67,0:13:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}因为我害怕对别人下杀手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.93,0:13:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但其实错的是我 我下一次绝对会开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.27,0:13:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我没说过什么才是真正正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这种事我也不知道 你真的就是错的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.36,0:13:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}好了 是时候打听一下关于他们的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.08,0:13:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}等等 我只是被雇来驾驶马车运送的老头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.09,0:13:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我见过你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.88,0:13:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}别人在街上叫他会长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.01,0:14:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}嗯 我认识他 迪墨·利布斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我只是遵从了中央宪兵的命令 而且我们失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.07,0:14:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}利布斯商会接下来全部财产都会被没收
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.49,0:14:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我跟那边的蠢儿子自不用说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.53,0:14:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我的手下也会被卷进某种事故里死掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.91,0:14:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那你就这样乖乖等死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.08,0:14:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}濒临崩溃的托洛斯特区之所以还能勉强维持运作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.71,0:14:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}很大的原因是利布斯商会给了很多人工作的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但如果商会没了 到底能有多少人能熬过这个冬天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.63,0:14:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}难道说 你要我们帮你们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们无论如何都要掌握艾连他们的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.93,0:14:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}身为宪兵御用商人的你们肯定能帮得上忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这样的话城镇和我的部下就不会饿死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.15,0:14:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我无法保证
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.94,0:14:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但你可以相信我会为此行动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.33,0:15:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}烦人的家伙终于回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.42,0:15:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}艾尔文 大事不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.29,0:15:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}事态恶化了 而且是两件事一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}第一件是艾连跟希斯特莉亚被抓了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.47,0:15:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我有三个部下被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.72,0:15:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我现在就要跟里维会合 无论如何都要找到他们的行踪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.14,0:15:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那么另外一件事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.81,0:15:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}艾连他回想起了尤米尔跟贝尔托特的对话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.73,0:15:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}如果这是事实的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我的脑袋就要炸裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.07,0:15:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.82,0:15:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}现在的问题是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.28,0:15:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不赶紧救出艾连 他就会被吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}喂 里维他们真的在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.09,0:15:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在的 我跟他们说好协助他们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.30,0:15:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他们才把我给放了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.80,0:16:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.19,0:16:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}利布斯 你这混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}对不起了 老爷们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.32,0:16:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这样的话我们真的可以得救吗 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}没人可以保证
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.91,0:16:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}怎么会 那为什么要帮他们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.79,0:16:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}对于商人来说最重要的是嗅觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不单单是眼前的金钱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}还要嗅到长远的得益之道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.17,0:16:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}一旦嗅到了就下定决心抓住这个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.51,0:16:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}懂了吗 给我记好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.26,0:16:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}久等了 还没结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.06,0:16:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}嗯 我也还不太习惯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.94,0:16:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}萨内斯 我也是个拷问人类的初学者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:16:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}请多关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.19,0:17:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}等等 把你的目的说出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}哪有人拷问不问问题直接用刑的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}也是啊 我有几个问题要问你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.99,0:17:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}艾连跟希斯特莉亚在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.54,0:17:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}为什么你们要盯上希斯特莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.66,0:17:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}雷斯家是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.04,0:17:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}太慢了 我们赶时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}又开始了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.76,0:17:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}总觉得惨叫声比兵长拷问的时候更大了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.01,0:17:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}虽然是为了救艾连他们 但还是很叫人消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.52,0:17:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们已经是罪犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.65,0:17:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}现在我们面对的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}并不是因为想吃掉我们才去杀他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}而是因为我们的思考方式不同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.45,0:17:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不对 也许仅仅因为我们的所属不同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.83,0:17:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}仅仅因为这样 我们就夺走了别人的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}阿尔敏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.00,0:17:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们已经不再是好人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.09,0:18:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}抱歉 我没萨内斯你拔得那么好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.88,0:18:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}到底要拔多少枚指甲才能那么熟练呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.26,0:18:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我数不过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你知道为什么在这狭窄的墙壁里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.81,0:18:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}至今都没有发生过战争吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.73,0:18:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那全都是因为我们第一宪兵不惜玷污双手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.73,0:18:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}才守护住这份和平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.90,0:18:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不管是那些自作聪明的教师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}想要翱翔天际的愚蠢夫妇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}还是躲在乡下牧场的妓女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.49,0:18:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}正因为我们消除了一切隐患
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.49,0:18:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}人类才走到了这一步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.50,0:18:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们理应得到人们的感谢！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.71,0:18:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}像你们这种一脸愉悦地伤害他人的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.88,0:18:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我从来没有见过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你们就是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但是我一点都不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.55,0:18:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我…我还有王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我相信着这面墙壁内的安宁与王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.14,0:18:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们所做的一切都没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.19,0:18:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}只不过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}没想到会是这么痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.90,0:19:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你们干脆把我折磨死算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.82,0:19:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这就是我沾满鲜血的全部人生了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}麻烦了啊 总觉得他好可怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.76,0:19:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}喂 别推我 好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.14,0:19:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}拉尔夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.51,0:19:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}没出息的家伙 才拔了一块指甲就全抖出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}萨内斯的指甲都被我们拔光了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.77,0:19:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}跟你完全是天差地别啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.23,0:19:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我管他 说不说是他自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那个热血混账满嘴都是王跟和平
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.24,0:19:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}对我们来说就是个累赘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.41,0:19:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}求求你们杀了他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.70,0:19:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在确认你的口供与他是否一致之前都不能杀他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}明明我坦白的事情都是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你们也太谨慎了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.67,0:20:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我说啊 我的牢房应该有床吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.98,0:20:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}来吧 萨内斯 我们重新打起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.61,0:20:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}虽然我也很不忍心 但我会努力拷问的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.32,0:20:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}雷斯家族才是真正的王室
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}真是的 我不想太引人注目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.25,0:20:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}弗雷盖尔那家伙跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.43,0:21:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你们商人的信用不是应该诚信的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.65,0:21:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不用打听一下里维的下落吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.90,0:21:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就算我们什么都不做他也会跑出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.65,0:21:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你很了解他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.36,0:21:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}毕竟是我教出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.62,0:21:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}里维·阿卡曼他就是一个这样的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.96,0:21:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}希斯特莉亚是正统王位继承者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.72,0:21:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.97,0:21:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}艾连和希斯特莉亚极有可能在罗德·雷斯手中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.44,0:21:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.78,0:21:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}希斯特莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.66,0:21:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}一直以来真是对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.68,0:23:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}少女的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.64,0:23:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那是足以动摇一国之王的巨大秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.02,0:23:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}得知这件事的艾尔文
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.48,0:23:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}回忆起了某一件往事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.23,0:23:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}下回 往事

